OL,3,CFuneral directors left decomposing
OL,4,Cbodies in un-cooled mortuary, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe bosses of a funeral directors
OL,8,Ffailed to buy a coffin for an elderly
OL,9,Fman and left his decomposing body in
OL,10,Fan uncooled mortuary room with water
OL,11,Fdripping down the walls, a court has
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FRichard Elkin, 49, and Hayley Bell,
OL,15,F42, who ran Elkin and Bell Funerals in
OL,16,FGosport, Hampshire, are on trial at
OL,17,FPortsmouth Crown Court accused of
OL,18,Fpublic nuisance, preventing lawful
OL,19,Fburial of a dead body and fraud.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/14
