OL,3,CFuneral directors left decomposing
OL,4,Cbodies in un-cooled mortuary, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FLesley Bates KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,8,Fjury that the bodies of two elderly
OL,9,Fmen were found on 10 December 2023 by
OL,10,FHigh Court enforcement agents who had
OL,11,Fbeen tasked with repossessing the
OL,12,Fpremises because of unpaid rent and
OL,13,Fdebts.
OL,15,FShe said the bodies were those of
OL,16,FWilliam Mitchell, 87, and Clive
OL,17,FReynolds, and explained that Mr
OL,18,FMitchell's body "showed obvious signs
OL,19,Fof decomposition".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/14
