OL,3,CFuneral directors left decomposing
OL,4,Cbodies in un-cooled mortuary, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe jury was also told that there had
OL,8,Fbeen five previous reports of "badly
OL,9,Fdecomposed" bodies at the premises
OL,10,Fdating back to July 2021.
OL,12,FMs Bates said: "Water was coming in
OL,13,Fthrough a leak in the roof of the
OL,14,Fmortuary room, it was running down the
OL,15,Fwalls.
OL,17,F"The room was not refrigerated, the
OL,18,Ftemperature within the mortuary room
OL,19,Fwas no different to elsewhere in the
OL,20,Fpremises."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/14
