OL,3,CFuneral directors left decomposing
OL,4,Cbodies in un-cooled mortuary, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe court heard that Mr Mitchell's
OL,8,Fbody remained in the mortuary room for
OL,9,F36 days and Mr Elkin told police that
OL,10,Fthe cremation had not taken place
OL,11,Fbecause they had not received payment.
OL,13,FBut Ms Bates said that Mr Mitchell had
OL,14,Ftaken out a funeral plan with Golden
OL,15,FCharter Ltd, and the defendants had
OL,16,Fbeen paid #2,040 to pay for the
OL,17,Fcremation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/14
