OL,3,CFuneral directors left decomposing
OL,4,Cbodies in un-cooled mortuary, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe court heard Bell then provided an
OL,8,Finvoice to Mr Mitchell's sister-in-
OL,9,Flaw, Patricia Mitchell, for the sum of
OL,10,F#1,295, saying that a coffin of
OL,11,F"simple design" would be provided,
OL,12,Fwhile telling Golden Charter it would
OL,13,Fbe "fully lined, oak veneered MDF
OL,14,Fcoffin", when no coffin had actually
OL,15,Fbeen purchased for Mr Mitchell.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/14
