OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMs Bates said the funeral directors
OL,8,Fhad been insolvent "almost since it
OL,9,Fbegan in 2019" and its "business model
OL,10,Fwas a case of robbing Peter to pay
OL,11,FPaul".
OL,13,FShe said the company owed #13,440 in
OL,14,Frent arrears and #8,567 for
OL,15,Felectricity.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/14
