OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMs Bates told the jury that three of
OL,8,Fthe previous cases of decomposed
OL,9,Fbodies found at the premises ` those
OL,10,Fof Jake Robertson, Diane Corbett and
OL,11,FMelvyn Marsh ` date from before 28
OL,12,FJune 2022 which is the earliest date
OL,13,Fthat the crime of public nuisance came
OL,14,Finto force.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/14
