OL,3,CFuneral directors left decomposing
OL,4,Cbodies in un-cooled mortuary, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe other two affected bodies were
OL,8,Fthose of Patricia Williams who died in
OL,9,FJune 2023 and Michael Clements, who
OL,10,Fdied in July 2023, and form part of
OL,11,Fthe prosecution case and their
OL,12,Fcondition was noticed when taken to
OL,13,Fhospital for a precautionary post-
OL,14,Fmortem examination.
OL,16,FMs Bates said there were more than 40
OL,17,Fother bodies stored at the funeral
OL,18,Fdirectors between 28 June 2022 and 10
OL,19,FDecember 2023 which were not seen at
OL,20,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/14
