OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FShe said: "Bearing in mind the
OL,8,Fcondition of the bodies they did see,
OL,9,Fwhat happened to these others?"
OL,11,FMs Bates said that the funeral
OL,12,Fdirectors was previously investigated
OL,13,Fby the Gosport Environmental Health
OL,14,FPartnership in August 2021 following a
OL,15,Fcomplaint by the family of Mr
OL,16,FRobertson.
