OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FNatalie Larkin, the goddaughter of the
OL,8,Fmother of Mr Robertson, had visited
OL,9,Fthe premises on 30 July and said: "I
OL,10,Fcould smell that smell of dead bodies
OL,11,Fbefore I even got to the door. When I
OL,12,Fwent in the smell was worse. I would
OL,13,Fdescribe it as being horrific."
OL,15,FThe family then removed Mr Robertson's
OL,16,Fbody and transferred it to another
OL,17,Ffuneral directors, Ruby Funerals.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/14
