OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe environmental health officers
OL,8,Fissued improvement notices on Mr Elkin
OL,9,Fand Ms Bell to make the mortuary "fit
OL,10,Ffor purpose" which Ms Bates said the
OL,11,Fdefendants initially complied with.
OL,13,FThis involved improving the
OL,14,Frefrigeration in the mortuary which
OL,15,Fthey did by purchasing a cooler on
OL,16,FeBay which was unsuitable because of
OL,17,Fthe size of the room, Ms Bates said.
