OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe defendants deny intentionally
OL,8,Fcausing public nuisance between June
OL,9,F2022 and December 2023, preventing
OL,10,Flawful burial of a dead body between 3
OL,11,FNovember 2023 and 11 December 2023,
OL,12,Fand carrying on a business
OL,13,Ffraudulently between 10 August 2022
OL,14,Fand 11 December 2023.
OL,16,FMr Elkin is also accused of using a
OL,17,Ffalse certificate of funeral directing
OL,18,Fon or before 10 December 2023.
OL,20,FThe trial continues.
